      concepts: [["Virtual address", "Address seen by process/JVM."], ["Page table", "Virtual page to physical frame mapping."], ["Page fault", "Trap into OS for missing/invalid mapping."], ["Swap risk", "Disk-backed paging is disastrous for cache latency."]],
      examples: [["JVM heap", "Reserved/committed virtual memory backed by pages."], ["Large cache", "Can pressure RAM and trigger reclaim."], ["Container", "Memory limits can cause OOM or heavy paging." ]],
